OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FGoldman Sachs to offer     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fsenior staff unlimited     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fholiday                    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Investment bank Goldman Sachs has said 
OL,6, its senior staff will be allowed to    
OL,7, take as much holiday as they want.     
OL,9,FThere will be no cap on paid leave     
OL,10,Funder the bank's new "flexible         
OL,11,Fvacation" plans which are designed to  
OL,12,Fpromote "rest and recharge".           
OL,14,FJunior bankers, however, will still    
OL,15,Fonly be entitled to a fixed amount of  
OL,16,Fholiday.                               
OL,18,FThe bank has been accused of           
OL,19,Foverworking younger staff in the past. 
